ZCZC PL29
NETHERLANDS COASTGUARD
NAVIGATIONAL WARNING - ADDITIONAL NR. 29 290012 UTC OCT
CONTAINER VESSELS WITH A LENGTH OF 100-200M
ARE AT RISK OF LOSING CONTAINERS DURING HEAVY SEA CONDITIONS
IN PARTICULAR FROM A WEST-NORTHWEST TO NORTHERLY DIRECTION.
THESE VESSELS SHOULD ALTER COURSE IF NECESSARY TO
AVOID COMING ABEAM TO THE WAVES AND TAKE OTHER APPROPRIATE MEASURES TO
AVOID LOSING CONTAINERS.
